<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idef6e9055-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s2151"><num value="2151">§ 2151.</num><heading> Rules and regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary is authorized to promulgate such rules, regulations, and orders as he may deem necessary in order to effectuate the purposes of this chapter.</p>
